href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-verve">The Verve</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/primal-scream">Primal Scream</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MY-CHEMICAL-ROMANCE">My Chemical Romance</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-bowie">David Bowie</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/madonna">Madonna作为灵感</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3832289" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3832289" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3832289" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Yungblud.-CREDIT_-Didier-Messens_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3832289" class="wp-caption-text"> Yungblud。信用：迪迪埃·梅斯斯/盖蒂图像</figcaption></figure><p>哈里森指出，唱片的咒语将是：“彼此聚在一起，看着对方，成为人类”，而不是说：“操你，这是我们必须实现的世界。”</p><p>在谈到概念专辑的想法时，他继续说：“这是&#39;tommy&#39;，这是一个&#39;四季度&#39;[ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/THE-WHO">who</a> ]。这是&#39;opera on the opera&#39;&#39;[queen&#39;[queen]。这是一个&#39;黑人游行&#39;[<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/MY-CHEMICAL-ROMANCE">我的化学浪漫</a>&#39;。这是“城市赞美诗”。 前。”</p><p>在其他Yungblud新闻中，今年夏天，Doncaster歌手将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-announces-bigger-and-better-bludfest-2025-get-ready-buy-tickets-3822031">他自己的节日的第二部分Bludfest</a>演出，该节目还将看到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chase-atlantic">Chase Atlantic</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/DENZEL-CURRY">Denzel Curry</a> ，Blackbear， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackbear">Blackbear</a>和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/the-cover">NME Cover Cover Stars</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/RACHEL-CHINOURIRI">Rachel Chinouriri</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peach-prc">Peach Prc的</a>露面。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fyungblud-tickets%2Fartist%2F5238519" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处</a>的门票。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/yungblud-responds-emotional-fan-says-he-saved-their-life-3850924">Yungblud对情感迷的帖子说，他“拯救”了他们的生命：“也许音乐是原声带，但您挽救了自己的生命”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
